{"tid":2511531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恥辱！俄羅斯舉行軍演 軍艦導彈被直播發射失敗！空中打轉後跌落海","createTime":"2021-05-01T03:50:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T04:38:01.000Z","uid":391580,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"32fc7b6e68ad816f9d059dcc5b0a9602ce1ef2a4","tid":2511531,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T03:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWKN6CRreA1e5FgzzjoLmJcKXS1SzSuQvKYbmsihEuepu?filename=ipmCbxQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FipmCbxQ.gif&h=5aa16dad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&ldquo;防務博客&rdquo;網站4月29日披露了一段俄羅斯海軍艦船在試射導彈時發生意外的畫面。當時俄羅斯海軍的&ldquo;沙波什尼科夫元帥&rdquo;號大型反潛艦在試射中發射了一枚&ldquo;口徑&rdquo;巡航導彈，但以失敗告終。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbF6PNZwVD9FaaVyTqZS2KHNQhDgxeDcYSZUQirLMcTtX?filename=4hHedMf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4hHedMf.jpg&h=458d6456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畫面顯示，這枚&ldquo;口徑&rdquo;巡航導彈幾乎是在發射後就出現失控，在上升過程中螺旋打轉，最終在軍艦的旁邊墜入海中。報道稱，這起事故沒有造成軍艦損壞和人員傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，&ldquo;口徑&rdquo;導彈是俄羅斯最新研制的巡航導彈，俄軍新銳護衛艦基本都配備了這款遠程打擊武器，俄軍也正在對多款老式戰艦進行升級改造，加裝&ldquo;口徑&rdquo;導彈。&ldquo;沙波什尼科夫元帥&rdquo;號屬于1155型無畏級法型反潛艦，隸屬于波羅的海艦隊。根據俄羅斯國防部網站的最新消息，該艦近日完成了曆時5年的升級改造，加裝了&ldquo;口徑&rdquo;和&ldquo;天王星&rdquo;巡航導彈系統，正式加入太平洋艦隊的常規戰備編組。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVjGvk5c8V6whXPWt7JZjHiFupCLWxcS2WNdBj5QKHUoe?filename=Q9vzdMo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ9vzdMo.jpg&h=46b6a5da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另據塔斯社4月6日的報道，&ldquo;沙波什尼科夫元帥&rdquo;號反潛艦在日本海進行海試時，首次使用了&ldquo;口徑&rdquo;巡航導彈對目標進行打擊。根據俄羅斯國防部的說法，在此次試射中，&ldquo;口徑&rdquo;巡航導彈精確命中目標，攻擊距離超過1000公裏。"},{"pid":"896dce66ced525c5e68c2746e1792e1ec0348046","tid":2511531,"uid":343017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T03:52:04.000Z","msg":"咁先唔會比人攔截到<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"320b4d19a7a2f3b9104decbb10cbaf405b3a002b","tid":2511531,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"896dce66ced525c5e68c2746e1792e1ec0348046","tid":2511531,"uid":343017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T03:52:04.000Z","msg":"咁先唔會比人攔截到<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T03:56:21.000Z","msg":"射十支，九支打轉自爆，得一支上到高空，仲唔玩死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c22d105fa1c3996ac112360d1f84ff75de2933","tid":2511531,"uid":258903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T04:04:10.000Z","msg":"俄爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88edbc8329ef323819a432a00ba39c5d82d465b","tid":2511531,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T04:34:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef09904fe4af15efabbdd4ba9a6c2d9fbb2c3f30","tid":2511531,"uid":375068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c88edbc8329ef323819a432a00ba39c5d82d465b","tid":2511531,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T04:34:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T04:35:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c88d5772e944de43d6373d09ae2e79a95928a7","tid":2511531,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T04:35:34.000Z","msg":"好撚肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa